#ad A lot of our fall Saturday evenings look like this, but this is the first time we’re trying out an Apple Cider Margarita with our @astraltequila and it is so good! If you’re looking for a new fall cocktail to try on the weekend, I recommend this. Full Recipe below. Cheers! 🍂

Apple Cider Margarita
1 ounce Astral Tequila Blanco
1/2 ounce orange liqueur
3 ounces apple cider
1/2 of a lime juice
1 tsp maple syrup
shake and pour over ice
cinnamon sugar rim
garnish with an apple slice & cinnamon stick

ASTRAL Tequila. 40% Alc/Vol. Diageo, New York, NY.

#ad I found the perfect holiday cocktail to make with your @astraltequila blanco! It's easy to make, tastes amazing with the bright and citrus flavor of the tequila, and looks festive. The Pomegranate Paloma is a way to put a little holiday twist on the classic paloma. And I love the rosemary sprig garnish! Swipe for the full recipe and save it to try yourself. Cheers!

Pomegranate Paloma
1/4 cup pomegranate juice
2 tbsp lime juice
2 tsp simple syrup
1.5 oz Astral Tequila Blanco
1/4 cup club soda
salted glass rim
rosemary sprig garnish

Enjoy responsibly. Do not forward to anyone under 21. ASTRAL Tequila. 40% Alc/Vol. Diageo, New York, NY.

We love it here! Follow along in our stories today to see what activities we’ll be hitting up today!

Great Wolf Lodge in 30 Seconds! ✨

We always have the best family time when we spend a weekend at @greatwolflodge With work and school during the week sometimes it feels like we’re all always on the go and there’s little time for bonding. #GRWU We’re heading to the Christmas Spectacular Starring The Radio City Rockettes in the new 2024 Lexus TX 550h+! #LexusPartner What a smooth and spacious ride it was into the city. I’m not gonna lie - one of my favorite features was the heated steering wheel - especially this time of year!

Some of my immediate fave features are the 14 inch touchscreen, that heated steering wheel, the digital rearview mirror and the wireless charger. It was definitely one of the most spacious mid-size third row seating SUV’s I’ve ever been in, and this Nightfall Mica color👌🏻#ExperienceAmazing
